                "name": "Before Combat",
                "text": " This furtive killer disguises herself as a human while stalking her targets. If at all possible, she avoids conflict, though her hunger sometimes gets the best of her."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "During Combat",
                "text": " If her presence is detected, the murderer begins combat by casting <i>confusion</i>. She then starts a bardic performance (typically dirge of doom). Before she actually enters melee, she casts <i>allegro</i> to gain additional attacks."
            }
